-- African Development  Approves $550 Million Loan for Egyptian Power Plant
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2010-12-24T11:46:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-24/african-development-approves-550-million-loan-for-egyptian-power-plant.html
The African Development Bank said it
approved a $550 million loan for Egypt to help the country build
a 650 megawatt gas-fired power plant.  The loan is the biggest ever given to Egypt by the Tunis-
based bank, it said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  